  "research_interests": "My doctoral document explored the application of pedagogy by Stanislavski, Meisner, and Chekhov in music performance and its scientific basis in neuroscience and psychology. My other studies included countertenor, jazz, improvisation, crooning, female belting, and Italian-American Music.",
